  "intent": "Execute a mass spectrometry sample preparation protocol using CSV-defined sample mapping. Transfer 30\u00b5L aliquots from 2mL tube racks to 96-well deep well plates maintained at 4\u00b0C using temperature modules. Perform pre-wetting with each sample transfer, then dispense to destination wells at 12.5mm height with dual blow-out and touch-tip. Following sample transfers, use multichannel pipette to dispense 90\u00b5L acetonitrile to all columns of the destination plate for protein precipitation, incorporating 10\u00b5L air gaps and pre-wetting steps throughout.",
